<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Gallery Magick Image CMS Plugins</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Gallery Magick Image CMS Plugins">
      <subsection name="Introduction">
        <p>
          Gallery Image Processing CMS Plugins provides plugins for Hippo CMS Authoring application,
          using <a href="../core/index.html">Gallery Image Processing Core Library</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          This library provides the following plugin components:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>MagickCommandGalleryProcessorPlugin</strong> : GalleryProcess service plugin
            which reads configurations, instantiates <strong>MagickCommandGalleryProcessor</strong>
            and register it as a <code>GalleryProcessor</code> service component for Hippo CMS Authoring application.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>MagickCommandGalleryProcessor</strong> : <code>GalleryProcessor</code> service component implementation.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>

  </body>
</document>
